{"tid":554229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國公安監控新科技　戴黑超掃瞄群眾捉疑犯","createTime":"2018-02-08T10:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T10:51:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4c85f98d86ac49a61f08c6269ac65c59979745","tid":554229,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T10:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180208/s00004/9033644cf2efd3a75b6f5ae3f43a9c68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180208%2Fs00004%2F9033644cf2efd3a75b6f5ae3f43a9c68.jpg&h=ecdb90b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴「黑超」未必為了看起來更有型，可能是為了拘捕犯人！外國媒體報道，中國鄭州公安開始配戴特殊的太陽眼鏡，可以在拍下疑犯照片，並連結到中央數據庫，可以在數秒內完成配對過程；如資料脗合，數據庫會提供疑犯的資料予警員。<br />\n<br />\n據指，這種方法已幫助警方成功拘捕了7名犯人，當中有人干犯人口販賣罪行，另外亦發現26人使用假冒的身分證。惟這項科技亦遭到人權組織質疑，國際特赦組織認為，這種人面識別技術，令中國的監視更加無處不在，將對異見人士及少數族裔不利。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司報道，中國目前有1.7億部閉路電視正在運作，預計未來3年將新增4億部。<br />\n<br />\n(英國廣播公司/商業內幕/自由時報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180208/s00004/1518083419103\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180208%2Fs00004%2F1518083419103&d=dgvwQtRVwxUBrRXODtoMvZzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=d11e7e7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180208%2Fs00004%2F1518083419103&h=bec9366e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180208/s00004/1518083419103</a>"},{"pid":"31c366f2bab2dd35c37e12d9951195f4371b5335","tid":554229,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T10:15:53.000Z","msg":"老大哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c945ab556f142d0efb10a0d647cc3687cdd8a2","tid":554229,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T10:19:24.000Z","msg":"將對異見人士及<span style=\"color: red;\"